
[Central themes to Aztec religion](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or6W4sXpl3c)
1. Humans are indebted by blood to the gods.
2. The sun needs human sacrifices to have the next day
3. human sacrifice is the most venerated way to honor the gods and the most valuable offer in exchange for something else
4. If there are no sacrifices, humans will die (occurred in the Second Sun)